item.title: It's no longer difficult to choose dog food, take a look at the Aide Italia air dry food.
item.author: youremail@domain.com (Some Person)
item.description: Nowadays, food safety is such a serious problem that everything we eat must be safe. As for the dog food, there are some unscrupulous peddlers who, in order to earn money, make “poisonous dog food” at low prices to attract consumers. The dog eating “poisonous dog food” for a long time not only does not get good nutrition, but also may increase the risk of physical illness. So, the shovel officer in the dog selection dog food must be careful and careful.
